## Status: Fine — QA comment (mandatory contract)

When **all** planned agent work for an **eversis-implement** thread is finished:

1. Declare **`Fine`** explicitly.
2. **In the same assistant response**, draft the QA comment following the **`eversis-fine-handoff`** skill (`eversis_skills_get` via MCP, or read `.cursor/skills/eversis-fine-handoff/SKILL.md` when vendored).
3. Label: **`Draft QA comment — review before posting to Jira`**
4. **Never** post to Jira in that turn; publication only after explicit human approval.

See upstream framework docs (`website/docs/workflow/overview.md`) for the full workflow contract.
